title: Smoke in AMK MRT station
full_title: Smoke in AMK MRT station
abstract: An SMRT maintenance worker was taken to hospital for smoke inhalation yesterday afternoon after the motor bearings of an escalator are believed to have overheated, emitting smoke inside Ang Mo Kio MRT station. A section of the station was cordoned off, but train services were not affected, SMRT said. FOR MORE ...
